|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|

|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|  Acceptance Criteria                                                                                                        |

| Outcome [action result]     |                                                                                             |

Please write in [TARGETLANGUAGE] language.

The user stories are under the table format.
title: Create A User Story
